Q: On May 9th, 2017 Jane bought 40 eggs. She ate one per day. Today she ran out of eggs. What is the date today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If Jane ate one egg per day, then she ate 40 eggs in 40 days. If today is the day she ran out of eggs, then today is 40 days after May 9th, which is 06/18/2017. So the answer is 06/18/2017.

